properties.name: Alcohol Bar
properties.description: Posted by NetwingDusni 6, pragThe Alcohol Bar is located 5 minutes walk from the Old Town Square. It has a sophisticated, intimate feel and is a great place to enjoy a cocktail from the selection of over 400 on offer. There are wooden tables and bar stalls to sit on while you sift through the book-like drinks menu. The mood is relaxed, with good music and subdued lighting. Later on in the night, the music picks up the pace a little. Though if you’re tempted to get up and dance, you’re probably best moving elsewhere. The Alcohol Bar is a fashionable venue, popular with an international crowd. Couples and small groups will find it the ideal place to sip on a cocktail, but it may take you a while to decide which one to go for!

properties.name: Aloha Wave Lounge
properties.description: Posted by NetwingDusni 11,pragAloha Wave Lounge is tucked away on a quiet street in the Old Town, less than 5 minutes walk from the Old Town Square. Aloha\'s Hawaiian cocktail bar theme adds an exotic touch to this easy going, friendly venue. Along the Hawaiian lines, there are even garlands for sale behind the bar. In the tradition of a good European music bar, things tend to liven up as the evening progresses, and after a few Pina Coladas people gravitate towards the small dance floor. Thursdays is live band night and at weekends there’s usually a DJ to put you in the party mood. The wood and brick interior at Aloha is welcoming. The dimmed lights and large selection of exotic cocktails give it a relaxed ambience. With its good selection of fruity cocktails, beers, wines and spirits, all at reasonable prices, Aloha is a fun place that is well worth a visit.

properties.name: Barock Restaurant
properties.description: Posted by Netwing Parizska 24,pragBarock Restaurant is located on Prague\'s most fashionable avenue, Parizska (Paris street). This smart, modern restaurant is dedicated to the stars of film and music. Enter by the glass doors and a bright and pleasant mix of reds and oranges greets you. The wood is fashionably dark and the lighting brings out the best of the photographs lining the walls. Czech celebrities such as Simona Krainová and Dara Rollins, along with American actors like Matt Damon feature in the shots; all are regular visitors to Barock Restaurant when they are in town, as are several other well known models and actors. The restaurant offers a good choice of International cuisine, ranging from Japanese sushi and Thai curry to Chilean sea bass, grilled gambas, scallops, steak and lamb chops. There are also salads, spicy soups and home made pasta. In the warmer months Barock offers pavement dining with heaters on Parizska. Opposite is it\'s sister restaurant: Pravda Restaurant. For a pre-dinner drink, Barock has a bar at the front of house specialising in exotic cocktails. Ambient tunes provide some cool, background music. Barock is a modern, ambient restaurant and bar, offering style and terrific food in a fine location. Remember to take a good look around; you never know who might be sitting at the next table!

properties.name: Bombay cocktail bar
properties.description: Posted by NetwingDlouha 13,pragBombay Cocktail Bar is a lively music bar, just a short walk from the Old Town Square along popular Dlouha street. It’s a busy place, but big enough to cope with its popularity. Bombay offers a good party atmosphere and attracts a large international crowd. There is space to dance if the mood takes you. You won’t have trouble getting to the bar, as it stretches right along one side of the room. Bar tenders expertly prepare delicious cocktails, some of the best in town. Of particular note are the Rum Runners and the Margaritas. They also serve a good range of beers from around the world. Bombay is a fairly large place, with exposed brickwork, high ceilings and archways separating the bar from the small dance floor. There’s a policy of no stag parties, but any groups entering in small numbers should be OK. Start off your night here, or come later on. It’s guaranteed to put you in the party mood.

properties.name: Bugsy's
properties.description: Posted by NetwingParizska 10,pragBugsy’s is an up-market cocktail bar located just down from the Old Town Square, on the exclusive shopping street of Parizska. As the name suggests, the bar has a 1950s American theme. Cocktail waiters in braces and bow ties prepare the drinks. Candles and cocktail-lounge music completes the mood. The bar staff at Bugsy\'s Cocktail Bar are as professional and knowledgeable as they come. They’ve won more bartending awards than anywhere else in the country. When you watch them mix up your Margarita, you’ll see why. The cocktail list includes all varieties imaginable. There’s over 200 to choose from, so your favourite one is sure to be there. As the atmosphere is relaxed and sophisticated, Bugsy’s is most suitable for couples and small groups of around 4 people. It’s a great place to spend a relaxed evening, or have a couple of cocktails to start off your night.

properties.name: Duplex
properties.description: Posted by NetwingVáclavské 21,prag Praha 1 Václavské nám. 21 Prague, Telephone: +42 02 2423 2319 Hours:Sun-Thu 10pm-3am; Fri-Sat 11pm-5am www.duplexduplex.cz In the heart of Wenceslas Square, perched on the top floors of one of the tallest buildings in town, Duplex is the most exclusive club in Prague, with spectacular views to match its status. A multi-level space with glass walls and a sprawling terrace, it draws moneyed ex-pats, hot young locals and more than a fair share of visiting DJs and celebs – decrepit rocker Mick Jagger had a birthday party here. Pricey drinks are well mixed by sexy young bar staff, and the lighting and sound systems are the most state-of-the-art in town. It’s all a far cry from its day job as a sophisticated café for the older, well-heeled set.

properties.name: Fluxiom
properties.description: Posted by Netwingfluxiom ist ein webbasiertes Digital Asset Management Tool für die Kreativ- und Marketingbranche ebenso wie für den privaten Nutzer. Es bietet eine elegante und einfache Plattform um Daten zu speichern, zu verwalten und zu verteilen. Digitale Assets wie Texte, Videos, Bilder und Präsentationen sind damit in jedem modernen Web-Browser ortunabhängig verfügbar. fluxiom unterstützt rund 100 Dateiformate und erzeugt automatisch Previews und Thumbnails für die Darstellung der Assets. Durch die Umsetzung mit innovativer Technologie entsteht eine Web-Benutzeroberfläche die einfach und schnell zu bedienen ist und sich vom “look-and-feel” herkömmlicher Web-Applikationen deutlich unterscheidet.

properties.name: Futurum
properties.description: Posted by NetwingZborovská 7,prag Praha 5 Zborovská 7 Prague, Telephone: +42 02 5732 8571 Hours:Mon-Sun 8pm-3am www.musicbar.cz/futurum/ Live music venue, nightclub and party spot that puts on local bands and hosts various other cultural gatherings. Locals love the futuristic-meets-industrial interiors, all exposed metal and brick and hi-tech lighting, perfect for the mini-warehouse style space. Drinks and friendly regulars apart it’s Friday nights that draw the crowds: retro-loving hipsters spinning to the 80s and 90s beats, and chatting to the young leggy blondes by the bar. Why not go over to one of them, look into her palm, and read her Futurum.
